2 period under section 47-30.2-04, before the date of the administrator's delivery of a
3 notice of an examination to a holder under this chapter.
4 3. The holder may satisfy the requirement to retain records under this section through an
5 agent.
6 4. The records must contain:
7 a. The verifiable information required to be included in the report;
8 b. The date, place, and nature of the circumstances that gave rise to the property
